Either way.. if you talk about the rights of innocent Americans and you support in ANY way the persecution, verbal or otherwise, of american citizens of arab origin (sorry if this is not pc term) then you are a HYPOCRITE and need to be persecuted to the fullest extent of the law.  You are NOT a patriot, and I venture to say that the dead in NY and DC would be ASHAMED of you.  <br>
